I've been getting this problem in Dawnshroud too recently. However I found the solution - Get Kodiacs and completely dominate the camp. I can kill every spawn with kodiacs and a manastone. They tend to lose interest fast if the most they can pull is a couple every 10 minutes.<br>
<br>
Of course when I've been camping it, I've explained to groups that I've got the camp. Then I get shit like 'I've never liked quadders, what entitles you to have them all'. I've never liked classes that can solo in dungeons, get groups easily or earn as much xp as I do quadding in a 2-3 person group in fungus grove, I don't try to pinch mobs from their camps however.<br>
<br>
Right now level 60 wizards have about 2-3 places to quad in luclin. Groups have a million places to go... <p><CENTER>
